indah di dunia.

1067
01:29:34.154 --> 01:29:36.989
Lama tak kudengar kabar
tentang Jenny...

1068
01:29:37.074 --> 01:29:39.617
...tapi aku sering memikirkannya...

1069
01:29:39.743 --> 01:29:43.204
